                    <span>Hey, look: Another book on writing with nothing new to say!
<br />
<br />Get Lukeman's two books and, if you've got a spiritual streak in you, Brenda Ueland's 'If You Want to Write' as well. </span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">You Don't Nedd to Read This One</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>2</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
